---

# TYPOGRAPHY

Font:

Inter

Optional Display Font:

Satoshi

Headings:

```txt
H1: 48px
H2: 36px
H3: 30px
H4: 24px
```

Body:

```txt
18px
16px
14px
```

Line Height:

```txt
1.5
```

---

# SPACING SYSTEM

```txt
4
8
12
16
24
32
48
64
96
```

Never use random spacing values.

---

# BORDER RADIUS

```txt
sm: 8px
md: 12px
lg: 16px
xl: 24px
2xl: 32px
```

---

# SHADOWS

Subtle shadows only.

Prefer:

```txt
shadow-sm
shadow-md
shadow-lg
```

Avoid:

Heavy shadows.

---

# COMPONENT RULES

All components must support:

- Light Theme
- Dark Theme
- Loading State
- Error State
- Disabled State
- Keyboard Navigation

---

# BUTTONS

Variants:

Primary
Secondary
Outline
Ghost
Danger

States:

Default
Hover
Pressed
Loading
Disabled

Buttons must:

- Have transitions
- Display loading indicators
- Have focus states

---

# INPUTS

Inputs must:

- Display labels
- Display helper text
- Display errors
- Support validation states
- Support keyboard navigation

Never rely only on placeholders.

---

# CARDS

Cards should:

- Have padding
- Rounded corners
- Hover effects
- Clear hierarchy

Use cards heavily.

---

# ICONS

Library:

Lucide Icons

Rules:

- 20px
- 24px
- Consistent stroke width

Never mix icon libraries.

---

# ANIMATIONS

Animation Philosophy:

Subtle and purposeful.

Never animate everything.

---

# DASHBOARD ANIMATIONS

Allowed:

- Fade In
- Slide Up
- Number Count
- Hover Elevation
- Skeleton Loading
- Tab Transitions

Duration:

```txt
150ms
200ms
300ms
```

---

# MOBILE ANIMATIONS

Allowed:

- Screen transitions
- Bottom sheet transitions
- Pull-to-refresh
- Progress animations
- Success animations

Avoid:

- Excessive parallax
- Heavy particle systems

---

# WEBSITE ANIMATIONS

Website should feel premium.

Allowed:

- Scroll reveal
- Parallax
- Mouse reactive gradients
- Floating elements
- Animated statistics
- Morphing backgrounds
- Timeline animations
- Animated maps
- Section transitions
- Smooth page transitions

Libraries:

Framer Motion
GSAP
Lenis

---

# PAGE STRUCTURE

Every page should follow:

```txt
Header
↓
Content
↓
Actions
↓
Footer
```

---

# EMPTY STATES

Every feature requires:

- Empty state
- Loading state
- Error state

Never show blank pages.

---

# TABLES

Requirements:

- Sorting
- Filtering
- Pagination
- Search
- Row Actions
- Responsive layout

---

# MAP DESIGN

Map should support:

- Dark Mode
- Light Mode
- Clustering
- Heatmaps
- Layer Toggles
- Marker States

Markers:

Pending
Verified
In Progress
Resolved

Each state needs a different color.

---

# DASHBOARD LAYOUT

```txt
Top Navigation
Sidebar
Page Header
Content Area
Right Utility Panel (optional)
```

Responsive:

Desktop First

---

# MOBILE LAYOUT

```txt
Stack Navigation
Bottom Tabs
Modal Sheets
Floating Actions
```

Bottom Tabs:

Home
Map
Report
Campaigns
Profile

---

# RESPONSIVENESS

Breakpoints:

```txt
sm: 640px
md: 768px
lg: 1024px
xl: 1280px
2xl: 1536px
```

Requirements:

Desktop
Tablet
Mobile

---

# ACCESSIBILITY

Required:

WCAG AA

Support:

- Screen readers
- Keyboard navigation
- Focus indicators
- Proper contrast
- Semantic HTML

Never use color alone to communicate meaning.

---

# LOADING EXPERIENCES

Prefer:

Skeleton loaders.

Avoid:

Spinners everywhere.

---

# FEEDBACK

All user actions require feedback.

Examples:

Success Toast
Error Toast
Progress Indicator
Confirmation Modal

---

# MICROINTERACTIONS

Use for:

- Button hover
- Card hover
- Successful report creation
- Donation completion
- Achievement unlocks
- Companion growth

Keep under:

```txt
300ms
```

---

# DESIGN TOKENS

All colors, spacing, typography and shadows must come from:

```txt
packages/ui
packages/theme
```

Never hardcode design values.

---

# FORBIDDEN UI PATTERNS

❌ Nested Modals

❌ Tiny Click Targets

❌ Infinite Scroll Everywhere

❌ Horizontal Scrolling Tables on Mobile

❌ Inconsistent Button Styles

❌ Multiple Floating Buttons

❌ Heavy Animations in Dashboard

❌ Cluttered Government Forms

❌ Random Colors

❌ Random Border Radius

---

# DEFINITION OF DONE

UI is complete only if:

✅ Responsive

✅ Accessible

✅ Consistent

✅ Animated Appropriately

✅ Loading States Included

✅ Error States Included

✅ Empty States Included

✅ Dark Mode Supported

✅ Mobile Friendly

✅ Production Ready

---

# FINAL RULE

Every screen should feel like a modern, premium smart-city platform rather than a traditional municipal system. The experience should make citizens trust the platform and enjoy using it while giving municipality operators powerful tools without overwhelming complexity.